Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:06.82,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always show my everything to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:10.90,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this moment was for me
